    "regional_variations": "Different providers by region: Honolulu Elderly Affairs Division (Senior Nutrition), Hawaii Dept of Health (Kupuna), Hawaii Meals on Wheels (Oahu), Lanakila Pacific, ALU LIKE (Native Hawaiian), Kaunona (Maui). Wait times may vary due to capacity.[1][3][6][8]",
